

1 Ni-wepnag: 

Am ant haꞌichu wo i em-oꞌohani ahni Peter mani d kehshaj g Jesus Christ. Heg at am i ni-kei mant wo i ahgahi ab amjed. Kuni haꞌichu s-em-ahgidamk ahpim mam am aꞌai kih Pontus ch Galasia ch Cappadocia ch Asia ch Bithynia jejewed ch ed hab masma mo g ni-wehm Tutuligo. 2 Jiosh at ab i em-gawulkai mamt d wo hemajkamgajk k ab em-mah g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag mat wo em-wehmajk ch am wo i kegch g em-dodakag. Mt hekaj ab wo s-wohog elidad g Jesus Christ ab i s-wohochudk mat iawua g e-ehꞌed k e muhkid em-wehhejed. 

Ab o wa si s-em-hoꞌigeꞌid g Jiosh ch ab wo wa baꞌich i em-mahkad g i wehmtadag ch s-ap tahhadkam. 

**Mach ab wui t-gewpkadch matt ep wo t-chegito **

3 Ab att hig wo si i hoꞌigeꞌel g Jiosh heg hekaj t-kownalig Jesus Christ. Heg ohg Jiosh at ab i wuhshad muhkig t amjed. K id am t-chehgidch mat hab waꞌap ab wo i t-wuwhas muhkig t amjed. Tt heg hekaj ab i s-wohochud k ab bei g wechij doakag. 

4 Jiosh o an nahtokch g si s-kehg kihdag am t-wehhejed an dahm kahchim ch ed. T ihda apꞌechudaj chum hekid d wo hekiakamk ch pi hekid wo e padch. 5 Ab ach s-wohochud g Jesus Christ. K heg hekaj t-nuhkud g Jiosh g si geꞌe e-gewkdagkaj. Kuch ab nenida mat s-ap wo maskogi g t-doꞌibiadag mat hekid wo huhug ihda jewed. 

6 Si g wo s-hehgigk mamt wo e doꞌibia, chum ams hems ab wo nakogad g nahnko mahs shoꞌigchudadag ch pi ap tahhadkam hemu. 7 Ihda em-shoꞌigchudadag at wo aꞌappe g em-wohochudadag k wo chehgi mo d wohokam hab masma mat g ohla g meikaj wo e aꞌappe mas d wohokam. Ia atsh ep wo i e chehgi Jesus Christ. T g Jiosh am haha wo chehgi mo ab si has em-elid. 

8 Pi am hi wa chum neid ch wabshaba ab si tatchua ch ab ep si s-wohochud. K id hekaj si geꞌej g s-em-hehgig. Kumt pi wo shaꞌi e nako mams wehs s-ap wo ah. 9 Jiosh at em-doꞌibia namt pi ab i s-wohoch g Jesus Christ. 

10 Hegam mash d Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam oki wa an oꞌohan matsh an wo em-ai ihda doꞌibiadag haꞌichu ahga ch eda an ep chum hoanahim g e-oꞌohana ch an chum mamche 11 mas hekid wo i k ch has masma hab wo e juh. Christ atsh ab ha mah g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag. Sh heg am ha tashogid matsh gam hu si ha baꞌich hab wo e juh matsh wo e shoꞌigch g Christ k haha wo bei g ab si has elidadag. 12 S-mahch ash mat pi wabsh hejel e wehhejed oꞌoha hegai mash am ha wui i e tashogid. 

Hemu at hab e juh hegai matsh wa an oꞌoha. K ahpim d em-wehhejedkam mamt wo kah. Jiosh chuhchai ash am em-ahgid ihda s-kehg haꞌichu ahgaj. K g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag ab ha mahkch g gewkdag mat an wo ahgahid. Ihda wohokam o shaꞌi si s-ta kakaima chum hems g anghil ha wehhejed. 

**Mattsh d wo chum si hekia s-apꞌekamk **

13 Am g wo i e nakog k ab wo si i e nenenashanichud k ab wo si i e gewpkai heg ab hoꞌigeꞌidadag mat g Jiosh wo em-mah mat hekid ep wo jiwia g Jesus Christ. 14 Ab g wo s-wohog elidad g Jiosh ch pi wo shaꞌi e hiwigi mams ged hu uhpam wo shul heg eda pi apꞌekam mam wa ab tatchua mam eda pi mahch g Jiosh. 15 Jiosh at ab i t-wai matt d wo hemajkamgajk. Kutt heg hekaj d wo chum si hekia s-apꞌekamk hab masma mo g Jiosh. 16 An o oꞌohanas Jiosh oꞌohana ed mo hab kaij: 

Hemho wa amt d wo hekia s-apꞌekamk nani pi ahni d hekia s-apꞌekam. *Leviticus 11:44-45 * 

17 Bam masma ihm g Jiosh ab e hoꞌigeꞌidahunch wui mo d em‑ohg. Kut heg wehs wo ha aꞌappe. Pegih, mt ab wo si has elidad chum hekid mamt heꞌes i tash ia d wo dodakamk. 

18 Heki o hu hab elidas mat wo em‑doꞌibia g heki hu em‑himdag. Em‑shohshonbad ash wa chum em‑mashcham mamtsh haꞌichu ab wo namkid g Jiosh k hekaj am wo i e apꞌech nenaj ed. Kumtp hems chum namkid g plahda o g ohla o wabsh chum haschu. K wabshaba ihda hab mahs haꞌichu d wabsh pi haꞌichu am Jiosh tahgio. Kum am hahawa s‑mahch mat g Jiosh baꞌich i s‑namkig haꞌichukaj em‑doꞌibia. 

19 Am o t‑tashogid g Jiosh mat has masma wo t‑doꞌibia am t‑chehanich mattsh wo mua g si s‑kehg kahwal k ab wui wo iagchul. Pegih, k g Jesus Christ d si hekia s‑apꞌekam ch hab sha masma e muhkid am t‑wehhejed mat wo t‑doꞌibia ab amjed g s‑koꞌok t‑namkidadag mach d pi ap chuꞌijkam. 20 Jiosh at am i kei mat eda koi in hu nahto g jewed k hemuch hahawa in i maskogi jewed dahm mat wo t‑doꞌibia 21 k ab i wuhshad am i dahm mat e muhkid k ab uhgk i be k ab dai e‑hugid an k ab si has elid. Kumt heg hekaj ab i s‑wohoch g Jiosh k ab si hiwig. 

22 Jiosh at ab i hekiagi g em‑doakag namt pi ab s‑wohog el g wohokam ab amjed. Pegih, ab g aꞌai wo e tatchuad wehs e‑ihbdagkaj. 23 Pi at hekid wo huhug g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga. Kutt ab i s‑wohochud k hekaj ab bei g wechij doakag. T id hab waꞌap pi hekid wo huhug, chum as g t‑chuhkug wo huhug. 24 Neh, an o hab chuꞌig Jiosh oꞌohana ed: 

Hemho wa at wehsijj wo koi g oꞌodham hab masma mat g washai wo gaksh. 

T g ha‑gewkdag wehs wo huhug hab masma mat g haꞌichu heosig. 

25 T wabshaba g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga pi hekid wo ha huhug. *Isaiah 40:6-9 * 

Neh, bo chuꞌig. K d hegai haꞌichu ahgaj mat am em‑wui e uꞌapa. 

